{"totalPage": 1, "totalElement": 12, "content": [{"id": 3, "createdAt": "2022-04-04T04:34:21", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:25:42", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "主题公园", "shortDescription": "轻松快速地新建和应用主题。通过从背景图像中提取颜色，它会自动新建一个适合用户风格的主题。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.themedesigner", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-1d33f9.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-211b54.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-63dd8b.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-9b17d2.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-b1189e.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-c1ea79.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-d23891.png"], "title": "使用背景图像新建主题。", "description": "<新建完整主题>\n- 根据您的壁纸使用自动推荐的颜色，或选择您想要的颜色，来新建主题\n- 按应用程序更改颜色，以符合您的品位\n- 在新建通用模式主题时，单独新建一个黑暗模式的主题\n\n<按照功能新建独立的主题>\n- 三星键盘：更改键盘背景以及每个按键的颜色、风格和图片以进行装饰）\n- 快捷设置窗口：自定义通知面板、快捷设置按钮和亮度栏\n- 音量控制窗口：自定义音量控制面板\n- 可以按应用程序排除主题的应用", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "壁纸;主屏幕;键盘"}, {"id": 46, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:53:50", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:27:16", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "EdgeLighting+", "shortDescription": "提供更丰富的侧屏闪光效果。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.edgelightingeffectunit", "thumbnails": [], "title": "", "description": "", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "通知"}, {"id": 47, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:54:27", "updatedAt": "2023-09-26T05:51:37", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Task Changer", "shortDescription": "这是一款操作更快、风格新颖的任务转换器。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.pluginrecents", "thumbnails": [], "title": "", "description": "", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1}, {"id": 48, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:55:10", "updatedAt": "2022-07-01T00:11:45", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Pentastic", "shortDescription": "将各种风格应用于 S Pen。您可以更改浮窗指令风格和 S Pen 指针的形状。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.pentastic", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-1cf212.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-430551.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-681358.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-93f5d3.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-b2896d.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-fe6529.png"], "title": "自定义 S Pen", "description": "- 更改浮窗指令风格和 S Pen 指针的形状 \n- 更改拉出 S Pen 时的声音\n- 用 S Pen 双击屏幕，启动应用程序快捷方式", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1}, {"id": 54, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:59:27", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:27:02", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "仙境", "shortDescription": "新建具有各种特效的 3D 动态壁纸。您可以在您收藏的图片上添加动态效果，使用贴纸、视频和文本来装饰您的壁纸，还可以添加粒子特效。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.wonderland.wallpaper", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-18803e.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-539c46.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-5d0ed6.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-672b43.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-7464e5.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-e017bc.png"], "title": "新建动态壁纸", "description": "- 给背景图像添加动态效果\n- 新建渐变背景\n- 添加粒子特效\n- 给人像模式照片壁纸添加 3D 特效", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "锁定屏幕;壁纸;主屏幕"}, {"id": 55, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:00:08", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:23:54", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "LockStar", "shortDescription": "新建锁定屏幕和息屏提醒风格。您可以将时钟、通知、应用程序快捷方式等每个组件整理到您所选的位置，并使用各种贴纸自定义锁定屏幕壁纸。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.systemui.lockstar", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-26d754.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-41d5df.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-6ae1f6.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-7a81ac.png"], "title": "自定义锁定屏幕和息屏提醒。", "description": "<锁定屏幕>\n- 选择各种时钟设计和尺寸\n- 重新定位锁定屏幕组件\n- 选择通知类型、图标颜色和尺寸\n- 调整锁定屏幕自动息屏\n- 使用贴纸进行装饰\n\n<息屏>\n- 推荐各种时钟风格\n- 选择显示或隐藏每个组件", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "锁定屏幕;通知;时钟;壁纸"}, {"id": 56, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:00:52", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:25:13", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Keys Cafe", "shortDescription": "设置为您优化的键盘，并尝试新建您自己独特的动画贴纸", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.keyscafe", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-1550b5.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-441189.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-5401fc.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-900889.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-95211c.png"], "title": "使用经优化的布局新建您的键盘，或使用各种图片新建您自己的贴纸集。", "description": "- 自定义您的键盘（添加/删除/重新排列）\n- 将按键大小调整为更宽或更窄\n- 给您的键盘应用新风格（颜色、按键效果和触摸音效）\n- 使用您的收藏图片新建贴纸集", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "功能扩展;键盘"}, {"id": 58, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:02:13", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:26:30", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "NavStar", "shortDescription": "方便地组织导航栏和手势模式。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.systemui.navillera", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-03522c.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-5b1220.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-5f1e64.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-6129c4.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-cbbdca.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-dc3291.png"], "title": "尝试新建您自己的导航栏或手势模式。", "description": "<导航栏>\n- 使用贴纸自定义导航栏图标\n- 添加实用功能按钮\n- 更改导航栏的背景颜色\n- 提供导航栏隐藏功能\n\n<手势模式>\n- 隐藏手势操作的背景\n- 调节手势手柄的长度和颜色\n- 通过“显示最近激活的应用程序”功能，在“Galaxy Fold”的导航栏中快速切换应用程序", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "手势"}, {"id": 60, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:03:42", "updatedAt": "2025-03-04T02:02:25", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Home Up", "shortDescription": "使用HomeUp创建您自己的OneUIHome。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.homestar", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-04-48086d.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-04-543d80.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-04-1e04b1.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-04-52379c.jpeg"], "title": "使用HomeUp创建您自己的OneUIHome。", "description": "- 使用DIY Home重新设计您的主屏幕\n-  创建自己的手势动画\n-  在主屏幕、应用程序和文件夹中使用各种布局\n-  自定义弹出式文件夹样式和布局\n-  恢复主屏幕布局\n-  自定义最近的应用窗口类型\n-  自定义您的边缘面板\n-  编辑通过共享窗口", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "主屏幕;手势"}, {"id": 62, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:05:10", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:24:55", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "ClockFace", "shortDescription": "您可以在锁定屏幕和息屏上配置多种不同的时钟风格，并根据需要自定义时钟。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.clockface", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-9ad1ed.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-24-20907d.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-24-7eb122.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-24-844c96.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2024-01-29-06a611.png"], "title": "选择您想要的时钟风格。", "description": "- 新建各种时钟风格\n ：选择您想要的时钟类型，并使用文本、图片或 GIF 进行装饰\n- 息屏时钟装饰\n- 将手表的时钟屏幕应用到设备（One UI 4.1 或更高）", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "锁定屏幕;时钟"}, {"id": 63, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:06:10", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:25:57", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "QuickStar", "shortDescription": "重新设计您自己的快捷面板用户界面 (UI)。您可以通过隐藏图标来简化状态栏，并更改快捷面板的主题。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.qstuner", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-261d72.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-9d2572.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-abc7d7.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-cc76e3.png"], "title": "您可以自定义状态栏和快捷面板设置。", "description": "- 隐藏状态栏上的图标 \n- 更改快捷面板主题\n- 按照传入通知的时间进行排序 \n- 在快捷面板中添加按钮网格选项（更宽或更窄）\n- 分左右打开快捷面板", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "时钟"}, {"id": 79, "createdAt": "2023-08-09T02:22:16", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:27:23", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Edge lighting+", "shortDescription": "在通知中添加您自己的个人风格。接收通知时享受趣味效果。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.edgelightingplus", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-09-0b5853.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-09-346692.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-09-925cf2.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-09-c1d086.png"], "title": "享受专属于您的个性化通知。", "description": "- 自定义接收通知时屏幕上显示的侧屏闪光风格\n- 按关键字设置风格\n- 使用表情符号/文本贴纸为通知提供情感表达方式\n- 仅在息屏状态下使用\n- 更改应用程序图标的图片\n- 从通知弹窗更改应用程序启动方法\n : 双击启动应用程序，防止向下滑动", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "makeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "通知"}]}